reviewText: This is very helpful if you are planning to trade futures especially the S&P500.  Entertaining and exciting speaker with a question and answer period at the end.

Lewis Borsellino, author of "The Day Trader: From the Pit to the PC" gives his 10 Commandments of Trading.  Mr. Borsellino tells some fascinating stories from his 20 years in "the Pit" on the floor of the the Chicago Merchantile.
